column5: Anyone know anything about this lake east of Nipigon off Hy 11? Thanks, Fishnut

My wife has fished there many times over the years with her family. They always stayed at Flayer's. I'll ask her to post some info when she gets home from work this afternoon. We've got maps of the area lakes there so she'll be able to name some spots for you.

FISHNUT I think there must be 2 Wintering lakes, the Wintering I fished is off Hwy 599 Ignace area. If this is the same lake let me know I have some good spots. Its one of my favorite lakes in Canada. Ginny Frank #844
